<sect1 id="installation">
<title>Installation Instructions</title>

<procedure id="install-procedure">
<step>
<para>Copy the directory tree from the tarball (or zip archive) to a location suitable for serving web pages.</para>
</step>

<step>
<para>With your web browser, go the location where you installed the package.  You will be presented with a web page that will help you configure and install the application.</para>
</step>

<step>
<para>After completing the installation, login and start reporting bugs.</para>

<note>
<para>Optional: Install JpGraph (<ulink url="http://www.aditus.nu/jpgraph/">http://www.aditus.nu/jpgraph</ulink>) if you wish to use it for the summary bug display on the home page.</para>
</note>
</step>

</procedure>

</sect1>

